snippet.title: One Night With Haro - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get It Here:
https://emmtyman.itch.io/onenightwithharo

One Night With Haro it's an Indie 2d-Action-Adventure video game
made by Emm Tyman in Madborn Studios. The story of this game
is about Greek Mystology in modern days! Explore, have fun and
chalenge yourself with Boss fights, learning skills and more!

Follow Emm Tyman:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/emmtyman/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EmmTyman

Follow Madborn Studios:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/madbornstudios/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/madbornstudios
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/user/madbornstudios

Follow One Night With Haro on Instagram
https://www.instagram.com/onenightwithharo
